messages.message:
Cypress on-call summary for Feb 3-7 :cypress-spin:

Cypress CI notes:
• `ground-truths-crud` was consistently failing and was fixed in https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/67679
• app creation was failing for about a day bc of a backend bug and was fixed in https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/67756
• `aihub-data-types` had a race condition that was fixed in https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/67818
• currently, custom function creation is broken in Cypress CI, but this should be fixed by https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/67864
aihub-sandbox notes:
• `upstream-integrations` has been failing for a few days because the `/api/v2/aihub/deployments/upstream-integrations/fetch` endpoint fails bc of an `Unsupported client` error (ss1, trace id: `a8ac0eda91f1a01a`) @Jessica 
• `search-app` has been failing because of a `ResponseStreamError` (ss2) @Subash 
• `payment` has been failing because of `no auth mechanism defined` error returned by Metronome (ss3) @Victor Zeng 
aihub-uat notes:
• `upstream-integration` has been failing bc of the same error mentioned above @Jessica 
• `search-app` is failing because a `data-testid="selection-group-Drives"` element can't be found (ss4) @Subash 
• `payment` has been failing bc of the same error mentioned above @Victor Zeng 
• there are some other flaky failures as well (example run (https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/17493/overview?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1)) 
    ◦ `aihub-data-types`, `aihub-refinement`@danny.lan
    ◦ `converse-project-crud` @Aayush 
    ◦ `results-table`, `file-list` @Udit
